jQuery Core
===============================================================================

This assembly provides access to jQuery APIs. This is only meant for use at
development time, so you can reference and compile your c# code against jQuery
APIs. You must include the appropriate jQuery scripts in your page for
runtime functionality.

More information is on http://jquery.com.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
